        "text": "Psalm 37:38",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") shows: his posterity. יהי להכרית is not merely exscindatur, but exscindenda sit (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
